# Data Dictionary

## Overview

This document explains the main tables and important columns used in the **PhonePe Financial Services Analysis Dashboard** project.

The purpose of this file is to make the dataset easier to understand and to show the structure behind the dashboard analysis.

---

# 1. `All_Users`

Contains user-level information.

| Column Name | Description |
|------------|-------------|
| `User_ID` | Unique identifier for each user |
| `Name` | Name of the user |
| `Age` | Age of the user |
| `Join_Date` | Date the user joined the platform |

---

# 2. `All_Transactions`

Contains overall transaction-level records across services.

| Column Name | Description |
|------------|-------------|
| `Transaction_ID` | Unique identifier for each transaction |
| `Amount` | Monetary value of the transaction |
| `User_ID` | User linked to the transaction |
| `Service` | Main service category used |
| `Service Type` | More detailed classification of the service |
| `Payment_Status` | Status of the transaction (Success / Failed) |
| `Reason` | Reason for payment failure or transaction issue |
| `Date` | Date of the transaction |

---

